{"TopicId":62591,"ForumId":39,"TopicTitle":"Messing Around with VTOL Planes","CreatedByName":"DVGamesInc","CreatedById":75322,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-02-09T00:09:47Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"DVGamesInc","CreatedById":75322,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-02-09T00:09:47Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EJeb and Bill decided to take their new VTOL planes out for a good flight, so I decided to take a few decent screenshots. \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003ESo here they are on the helipad prepping for takeoff.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/YOBsh9w.png\u0022 alt=\u0022YOBsh9w.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EMid-flight\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/AldLHcw.png\u0022 alt=\u0022AldLHcw.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EReturning after performing a very successful test flight.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/QN3mrLW.png\u0022 alt=\u0022QN3mrLW.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EAnd a final approach.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/SNY08Cy.png\u0022 alt=\u0022SNY08Cy.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003ELanded!\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/7QudzKO.png\u0022 alt=\u00227QudzKO.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EJeb proceeds to look off into the distance, getting a few.. uh.. ideas.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/xwDrNvC.png\u0022 alt=\u0022xwDrNvC.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EThen, after making a bet with Bill that he could fly under the arch at R\u0026amp;D, this happened...\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/lKX5WPq.png\u0022 alt=\u0022lKX5WPq.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EHope you enjoyed! \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Thomas988","CreatedById":92699,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-02-09T13:08:47Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EVery nice VTOLs! \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Rhyunix","CreatedById":59383,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-02-09T15:06:29Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EHow did you get them to fly simultaneously?!\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"DVGamesInc","CreatedById":75322,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-02-09T18:10:10Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EI flew both planes simultaneously simply by lowering their throttle to a little more than a hover and made sure to keep them within rendering distance. \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Patupi","CreatedById":71098,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-02-09T19:39:36Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EFlicking back and forwards between the two? Landing must have been tricky, watching the one up in the air while you were landing the first one to make sure it didn\u0027t drift into something... oh wait... that last picture \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Rhyunix","CreatedById":59383,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-02-09T19:43:53Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EI didn\u0027t think that you could swap whilst it was in the atmosphere?\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}